data.description:
Location, location, location.  This lovely condo is located in a very desirable area of Baymeadows/Mandarin, with access to all that San Jose has to offer. The kitchen has newer SS appliances, including a double oven. With two closets, the enclosed Florida room could double as a bedroom.  Updated flooring in dining & living areas. The electrical panel was replaced in 2018. The community has a number of nice amenities, including a clubhouse,, two swimming pools... one Indoor and one outdoor, a sauna, and tennis courts. Seller will be replacing the carpet in the bedrooms.  The grounds/lawn maintenance, trash pickup and insurance are all included in the monthly HOA fee. 
The condo is located in the rear of the complex, which is a very quiet area. Don't miss this one!
